{"tid":1429825,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴徒持有超嚴重攻擊性武器 並長時間照射警方 傷害警察健康","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:45:08.000Z","uid":229436,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8d898d3fd438c4d1833921fd64e85ec8d0ff0164","tid":1429825,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2016/01/1511151832542483-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2F1511151832542483-600x400.jpg&h=491b55ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太陽長時間照射警方全身及眼睛 令警察日光下工作困難 及 直視下眼睛會受傷<br />\n強烈要求警方嚴正執法 拘捕該太陽持有者及消滅太陽 以免眾多警員受其傷害</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接看太陽會造成視覺上的光幻視和暫時部分<span style=\"color: orange;\">失明</span>，只要4毫瓦的陽光對視網膜稍有加熱就可能造成破壞，使眼睛對光度不能做出正確的回應。暴露在紫外線下會使眼睛的水晶體逐漸變黃，並且被認為還會<span style=\"color: orange;\">形成白內障</span>，但是這取決於是否經常曝露在太陽的紫外線下，而不是是否直接目視太陽。儘管已經知道<span style=\"color: orange;\">暴露在紫外線的環境下，會加速眼睛外層的老化和白內障的形</span>成，當日食發生的時候還是有許多不當注視太陽所引發的日食目盲或視網膜灼傷。長時間用肉眼直接看太陽會受到紫外線的誘導，<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">大約100秒鐘視網膜就會灼傷產生病變</span>，特別是在來自太陽的紫外線強度較高和被聚焦的情況下；對孩童的眼睛和新植入的水晶體情況會更為惡化（它們比成熟的眼睛承受了更多的紫外線）、以及太陽的角度接近地平、和在高緯度的地區觀測太陽。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2598%25B3&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLCQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=7a9be43c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3</a>"},{"pid":"0020ea20c84472e57a97316383a773af6d0ac5dc","tid":1429825,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae7979ce0f0a6d13b2dd88d2fb562612389a1f8","tid":1429825,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}